lead_paragraph: China's Chen Ruolin and Liu Huixia claimed gold in the women's synchronized 10 metre platform diving event at the Rio Games on Tuesday, with Malaysia and Canada respectively taking the silver and bronze medals as the venue's pool turned a bright green hue.

headline.print_headline: China Wins Gold in Women's 10 Metre Synchronized Diving
